features: 【MFi Certified Lightning Cable】: Each cable is built-in MFi chip, no safety warning message pops up when in use.
【Compact & Portable】: The total length of this short iPhone charger cable is 1 foot from the USB A end to lightning end. Compact design allows you to carry it anywhere, and easy to store.

【3A Fast Charge & Sync】：This short lightning cable supports fast charging (up to 3A) and high speed data transferring (480Mbps). Aioneus recommended that you use the original plug or a charger with fast charging function to achieve 3A fast charging.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Just the right length
reviews.reviewText: I received a battery pack as a present for my iPhone. But all I had was a long cable. I used the long one several times, but I realized that I needed a shorter cable. I am glad that I ordered this pair of cables. They are exactly what I needed. Just the right length so I can carry it around. It works fine to charge up my phone! A very good product at the right price!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 5, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars It is magical this cable works for my iPhone X charger!
reviews.reviewText: Couple of months ago I replaced my iPhone X battery at Apple Store, but strange enough two chargers I have are no longer working, only one Apple Original charger is still working. I found the reason is due to usb port, only usb-c port is still charging my iPhone, the usb-a port is not working anymore for my iPhone X. Actually I was purchasing usb-c to lighting charging cable, but by mistake I bought this cable, which is usb-a to lighting cable. After I received this cable I tried it, the magical thing happened, it works! With this cable my other two chargers are working again. I don’t know the reason, but do appreciate the good quality of this cable!
